| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2936 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7c5ea20c-1d11-57d4-a419-5d322f5813db"
